2008年，拉格斐創作了一隻由{{le|Steiff|Margarete Steiff GmbH}}以他的形象製作的2,500隻泰迪熊，售價為每隻$1,500美元<ref>{{cite news |url=http://nymag.com/daily/fashion/2008/08/get_your_karl_lagerfeld_teddy.html |newspaper=New York Magazine |title=Get Your Karl Lagerfeld Teddy Bear for Just $1,500! |date=2008-08-22 |accessdate=2019-02-25 |archive-date=2012-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120614062833/http://nymag.com/daily/fashion/2008/08/get_your_karl_lagerfeld_teddy.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。每隻熊有多種方式使用，別針，襯衫，娃娃等<ref name="#2">{{cite web |url=http://www.sassybella.com/2010/01/karl-lagerfelt-the-finger-puppet/ |title=Karl LagerFELT the finger puppet |date=2010-01-26 |publisher=Sassybella.com |access-date=2011-10-24 |archive-date=2012-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120505151959/http://www.sassybella.com/2010/01/karl-lagerfelt-the-finger-puppet/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2009年，Tra Tutti開始出售卡爾·拉格鼠及卡爾·拉格斐，它們分別以小老鼠和手指木偶的形式出現的迷你版拉格斐<ref name="#2"/>。同年，他為法國動畫《{{le|完全是間諜|Totally Spies! The Movie}}》獻聲<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.premiere.fr/film/Totally-Spies-!-Le-film-1211476/(affichage)/casting |title=Le casting de Totally Spies ! Le film |author= |date= |work=Premiere.fr |access-date=2015-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402131825/http://www.premiere.fr/film/Totally-Spies-!-Le-film-1211476/(affichage)/casting |archive-date=2015-04-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

在晚年，拉格斐意識到其中一個自己少年時代的志向—成為一名專業的漫畫家，從2013年起，他的政治漫畫定期會於德國報章《[[法蘭克福匯報|法蘭克福匯報]]》上定期發表<ref>DW Documentary (2014), 5:35.</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/karl-lagerfeld-skewers-angela-merkel-political-cartoon-1048053 |title=Karl Lagerfeld Skewers Angela Merkel in Political Cartoon |author=Reed, Sam |date=2017-10-12 |website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |accessdate=2019-02-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190215101022/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/karl-lagerfeld-skewers-angela-merkel-political-cartoon-1048053 |archivedate=2019-02-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref> 。

